    <CardBody>
        <StandardCardTitle Title="Siri shortcut" TitleColor="TextColor.Info" />

        <CardText TextColor="TextColor.Primary">
            <Paragraph>
                For users with Apple devices, a Siri shortcut is available to quickly share text to the server.

                The shortcut can perform the peek, pop, push, and list entries actions and copies the fetched values to the clipboard.
                It is also also added in the share-menu for quick pushes to an id.

                You can download the shortcut from
                <Link TextColor="TextColor.Secondary"
                      To="https://www.icloud.com/shortcuts/689115cca5f849bd948233533b1362ba"
                      Target="Target.Blank">
                here
                </Link>,
                see the
                <Link TextColor="TextColor.Secondary"
                      To="https://github.com/RobinClaesson/TextShare"
                      Target="Target.Blank">
                GitHub README
                </Link>
                 for setup instructions.
            </Paragraph>
        </CardText>


    </CardBody>
</Card>
